<BLOCK1><TI TOCID="III"><UNDER>AFFIDAVIT</UNDER></TI>
<P>I, <BOLD>RONG WEI</BOLD>, housewife, of Vancouver, Province of British Columbia, SWEAR (OR AFFIRM) THAT:</P>
<P>1. I am the plaintiff in this action and as such have personal knowledge of the facts deposed to in this affidavit except where stated to be on information and belief and in which case I verily believe them to be true.</P>
<P>2. I have known the defendants Allan Chiu and Queenie Lau since 2014. In my first affidavit dated May 12, 2017, I described how I came to know Mr. Chiu and Ms. Lau. I also provided details of my dealings with them that gave rise to my claims against them.</P>
<P>3. I have retained John Hilpert, a private investigator, to conduct surveillance of Mr. Chiu and Ms. Lau. Mr. Hilpert has sworn an affidavit detailing his observations of Mr. Chiu and Ms. Lau on September 24, 26, 27, 28 and October 10, 2018.</P>
<P>4. I have reviewed Mr. Hilpert's Affidavit #2 dated November 1, 2018.</P>
<P>5. Based on my review of the photographs located at <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;A&rdquo;</BOLD> to Mr. Hilpert's Affidavit #2, I confirm that the individuals being photographed are Mr. Chiu and Ms. Lau.</P>
<P>6. Based on my review of the photographs located at <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;B&rdquo;</BOLD> to Mr. Hilpert's Affidavit #2, I confirm that the individuals being photographed are Mr. Chiu and Ms. Lau. I also confirm that the young woman approaching the black BMW vehicle in the last photograph is Mr. Chiu and Ms. Lau's daughter Romie.</P>
<P>7. Based on my review of the photographs located at <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;C&rdquo;</BOLD> to Mr. Hilpert's Affidavit #2, I confirm that the individuals being photographed are Mr. Chiu and Ms. Lau. I also confirm that the young woman photographed exiting and entering the BMW vehicle and sitting with Ms. Lau in the Point Grey Medical Clinic is Mr. Chiu and Ms. Lau's daughter Romie.</P>
<P>8. Based on my review of the photographs located at <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;D&rdquo;</BOLD> to Mr. Hilpert's Affidavit #2, I confirm that the individuals being photographed are Mr. Chiu and Ms. Lau.</P>
<P>9. Based on my review of the photographs located at <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;E&rdquo;</BOLD> to Mr. Hilpert's Affidavit #2, I confirm that the individuals being photographed are Mr. Chiu and Ms. Lau.</P>
