<BLOCK1><TI TOCID="IV"><UNDER>AFFIDAVIT</UNDER></TI>
<P>I, <BOLD>TINA LE</BOLD>, paralegal, of #900&mdash;980 Howe Street, Vancouver, British Columbia V6Z 0C8, AFFIRM THAT:</P>
<P><BOLD>1.</BOLD> I am a paralegal with the law firm of McEwan Cooper Dennis LLP, solicitors for the plaintiff, Rong Wei, and as such have personal knowledge of the facts and matters hereinafter deposed to save and except where stated to be based on information and belief and where so stated I verily believe the same to be true.</P>
<P><BOLD>2.</BOLD> Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;A&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an email chain between Owen James and Bill Riley dated June 21, 2017 regarding the authorization and amount of living expenses for Queenie Lau and Allan Chiu.</P>
<P><BOLD>3.</BOLD> Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;B&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an email chain between Mr. Riley and Mr. James dated June 21, 2017 regarding the authorization of living expenses for Ms. Lau.</P>
<P><BOLD>4.</BOLD> Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;C&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an email chain among Mr. James, Sabrina DiGiacomo and Mr. Riley dated June 22, 2017 regarding the authorization of living expenses for Ms. Lau.</P>
<P>5. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;D&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an email chain between Mr. Riley and Mr. James dated June 27, 2017 regarding the authorization of living expenses for Ms. Lau.</P>
<P>6. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;E&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an email chain between Mr. James, Ms. DiGiacomo and Mr. Riley dated July 13, 2017 regarding the authorization of living expenses for Ms. Lau.</P>
<P>7. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;F&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an email from Mr. Riley to Mr. James dated August <BOLD>2, 2017</BOLD> regarding payment of living expenses for Ms. Lau.</P>
<P>8. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;G&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an email from Mr. Riley to Ms. Lai dated August 22, 2017 regarding payment of living expenses for Ms. Lau.</P>
<P>9. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;H&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an email chain among Craig Dennis, Kieran Siddall and Mr. Riley dated October 3, 2017 regarding the defendants' proposal to vary the <EM>Mareva</EM> order.</P>
<P>10. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;I&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an email chain between Mr. Dennis and Mr. Siddall dated October 18, 2017 regarding the list of documents of the defendants and the scheduling of proposed examinations for discovery.</P>
<P>11. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;J&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an email chain between Ms. DiGiacomo and Nadine Abram dated November 3, 2017 and letter from Mr. Siddall to Ms. DiGiacomo dated November 3, 2017 regarding the release of funds for the living expenses of Ms. Lau.</P>
<P>12. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;K&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an email chain between Mr. Siddall and Mr. Dennis dated November 3, 2017 regarding the authorization of living expenses for Mr. Chiu.</P>
<P>13. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;L&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an email chain between Mr. Dennis and Mr. Siddall dated November 9, 2017 regarding the scheduling of examinations for discovery and the defendants' list of documents.</P>
<P>14. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;M&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an email from Ms. Abram dated November 23, 2017 and letter from Mr. Siddall to Kevin Ma and Peony Lo dated November 23, 2017 regarding the release of funds for the living expenses of Ms. Lau.</P>
<P>15. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;N&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of a letter from Mr. Dennis to Mr. Siddall dated July 5, 2018 requesting a copy of the defendants' documents from their list of documents dated July 3, 2018.</P>
<P>16. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;O&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of a letter from Mr. Dennis to Mr. Siddall dated August 1, 2018 following up with respect to receipt of the defendants' documents from their list of documents dated July 3, 2018.</P>
<P>17. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;P&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an email chain between Mr. Dennis and Mr. Siddall dated August 20, 2018 regarding the scheduling of the examination for discovery of Ms. Lau.</P>
<P>18. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;Q&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of a letter from Mr. Dennis to Mr. Siddall dated September 19, 2018 enclosing an appointment to examine for discovery issued to Ms. Lau and conduct money. I caused the appointment and conduct money in the amount of $20 to be delivered to Mr. Siddall.</P>
<P>19. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;R&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an invoice from Charest Reporting dated September 28, 2018 for a witness non-attendance fee.</P>
<P>20. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;S&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of an email chain between Mr. Dennis and Mr. Siddall dated October 1, 2018 regarding the scheduling of the examination for discovery of Mr. Chiu.</P>
<P>21. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;T&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of a letter from Mr. Dennis to Mr. Siddall dated October 4, 2018 regarding the scheduling of the examinations for discovery of Mr. Chiu and Ms. Lau.</P>
<P>22. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;U&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of a letter from Mr. Siddall to Mr. Dennis dated October 9, 2018 regarding the defendants' proposed variation of the <BOLD><EM>Mareva</EM></BOLD> order and scheduling of the examinations for discovery of Ms. Lau and Mr. Chiu.</P>
<P>23. Attached and marked as Exhibit &ldquo;V&rdquo; to my affidavit is a copy of a letter from Mr. Aitken to Mr. Siddall dated October 10, 2018 demanding that the defendants produce further documents.</P>
<P>24. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;W&rdquo;</BOLD> to my affidavit is a copy of a letter from Mr. Dennis to Mr. Siddall dated October 16, 2018 regarding the scheduling of the examination for discover y of Ms. Lau.</P>
<P>25. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;X&rdquo;</BOLD> is a copy of an email from Gail Major to Mr. Chiu and Ms. Lau dated May 19, 2017 attaching a letter from Mr. James to Mr. Chiu and Ms. Lau dated May 18, 2018 enclosing the order made after application of Madam Justice Humphries pronounced May 18, 2017.</P>
<P>26. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;Y&rdquo;</BOLD> is a copy of a Bank of China (Hong Kong) Ltd. A/C Financial History Transaction List dated from May 12, 2017 to July 31, 2017 for account holder Sung Fai Chiu, also known as Allan Chiu.</P>
<P>27. Attached and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;Z&rdquo;</BOLD> is a copy of the Bank of Canada exchange rate on May 19 to 22, 2017 for US dollar and Hong Kong dollar currencies.</P>
