<BLOCK1><TI TOCID="II">AFFIDAVIT</TI>
<P>I, Cara Echino, Process Server of 403 - 1228 Hamilton Street, Vancouver, BC, SWEAR (OR AFFIRM) THAT:</P>
<P>1. On November 22, 2018, I was instructed by our client Norton Rose Fulbright LLP to begin a rush skip locate of the Defendants Allan Chiu and Mui Kwan Queenie Lau also known as Mui Kwan Queenie Chiu.</P>
<P>2. I was provided with the following information:
<P1>a) Last known address of XXXXXXXXXX</P1>
<P1>b) Allan Chiu's email address is allan@allanchiuconsulting.asia</P1>
<P1>c) Telephone number for Allan Chiu is XXXXXXXXXX</P1></P>
<P>3. On November 23, 2018 at 5:07 p.m., a telephone call was made to XXXXXXXXXX. I received a message right away that said &ldquo;the customer you are calling is unavailable&rdquo;. I was unable to leave a message. An internal search was completed of the phone number and found that it is listed to &ldquo;King Ching Chan&rdquo;. A cross reference search was completed on that name, and we found no relation to Allan Chui or Mui Kwan Queenie Lau also known as Mui Kwan Queenie Chiu.</P>
<P>4. On November 23, 2018 5:09 p.m., an email was sent to allan@allanchiuconsulting.asia from an email address belonging to Mainland Delivery Services, in which I advised Allan Chiu of a delivery and provided a package ID number, and the link to tracking of the &ldquo;package&rdquo;. I advised that we attempted delivery at XXXXXXXXXX but was unable to deliver. I asked for a new address for delivery but have not received a response.</P>
<P>5. All preliminary and basic online searches were completed, which include but are not limited to, searching all social media platforms (Facebook, Instagram, Linkedin, etc.), BC OnLine name cross-referencing, myLTSA land and property records, Canada 411, and all City and utility public records. I report the following results:
<P1>a) Facebook profile found for Queenie Lau</P1>
<P1>A direct &ldquo;messenger&rdquo; message was sent to Queenie Lau at 5:52 p.m., November 22, 2018. As of 8:08 a.m. on November 23, 2018, the message showed as &ldquo;read&rdquo;, but no reply was received.</P1>
<P1>b) Various social sites for &ldquo;Allan Chiu&rdquo;, but it is unclear if it is the correct person (no picture to identify, etc)</P1>
<P1>c) Allan Richard Chiu located at XXXXXXXXXX listed as a &ldquo;Machinist&rdquo;. Unclear whether this is the correct person.</P1></P>
<P>6. We have been advised by a confidential and reliable source that a plate number check of the vehicles owned by Allan Chiu and Mui Kwan Queenie Lau also known as Mui Kwan Queenie Chiu are registered to the address of XXXXXXXXXX</P>
<P>7. We have also been advised that Mui Kwan Queenie Lau also known as Mui Kwan Queenie Chiu also sometimes goes by the name &ldquo;Suet&rdquo;. We have cross-referenced this name with all above sources and did not find any conclusive results.</P>
<P>8. At this time, we are unable to definitively locate Allan Chiu and/or Mui Kwan Queenie Lau also known as Mui Kwan Queenie Chiu, but believe that documentation would come to their attention if service was effected substitutionally, by leaving the documentation on the front door of the registered residential address of the Allan Chiu and Mui Kwan Queenie Lau also known as Mui Kwan Queenie Chiu, being the property located at XXXXXXXXXX</P>
