<P>2. The native language I speak is Cantonese. I have a basic grasp of the English language. The contents of this, my 3<SUP>rd</SUP> affidavit in this matter, were explained to my counsel and subsequently explained to me by my counsel with the assistance of Serene Chow, a Cantonese speaking lawyer at Boughton Law. Following the explanation, I advise that I understand the information contained in this affidavit as written in English.</P>
