<BLOCK2><TI><EM>Financial Records</EM></TI>
<P>5. In response to paragraph 42 of the Notice of Application filed February 5, 2019 (the &ldquo;<BOLD>Queenie Contempt Application</BOLD>&rdquo;), the plaintiff states that spending in excess of the monthly amount of $3,500 is outlined in appended Schedule &ldquo;B&rdquo;. I did not spend more than the allotted $3,500 per month and provide the specifics regarding the transactions as follows:
