<P>19. I did state that I was available for discovery between the dates of December 18, 2018 and December 20, 2018 and would attended whether ordered or in response to the appointment.</P>
<P>20. Unfortunately, as is particularized in the letters above, my health deteriorated to the point I was unable to attend and has continued to plague me through to today's date.</P>
<P>21. I swear this affidavit in response to the Notice of Application of the plaintiff in the above referenced action filed February 5, 2019.</P>
